<p>The Microsoft Office 365 integration for UCS allows to easily provision Azure Active Directory accounts with single sign-on for users.</p>
<ul>
    <li>To use this app, an Azure AD  administrator account is required. In addition, Office 365 licences are required for the account</li>
    <li>To test Microsoft Office 365 free of charge, a test account can be created at <a href="https://products.office.com/business/">products.office.com</a>.</li>
    <li>To create, modify and delete accounts, this app needs administrative access to the Azure Active Directory account. A <a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="require('umc/app').openModule('office365')">setup wizard</a> will guide you through the configuration process.</li>
</ul>
<p>Users need to be modified in the <a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="require('umc/app').openModule('udm', 'users/user')">Domain administration</a> in order to use this service.</p>
<p>Univention did not test <a href="https://support.office.com/en-us/article/Using-Office-365-modern-authentication-with-Office-clients-776c0036-66fd-41cb-8928-5495c0f9168a" target='_blank'>Office client integration, please refer to the Microsoft documentation</a></p>
